{"tid":1417377,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於「光復香港 時代革命」的定義","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T19:47:17.000Z","uid":260848,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ae1e62d29cbb7763046aa2c41570c4a8c61ca99c","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:28:18.000Z","msg":"呢個口號今晚引起爭論，其實係好事嚟<br />\n多d討論多d思考，唔好人嗌你又嗌<br />\n你又有冇諗過自己嗌緊乜？<br />\n唔好屌住先，我意思係，呢個口號確實係<span style=\"color: blue;\">相當空泛</span><br />\n既然係咁，我地係咪可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己定義咗佢先</span></span></strong>？<br />\n<br />\n反對口號既人認為，而加777想spin落港獨，呢個口號就係最明顯既佐證<br />\n不能否認呢一點，但係：<br />\n1. 呢個口號確實有氣勢有凝聚力，相信咁多人叫，叫得既大家都buy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 所以而加話唔叫係好多人都唔會跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得返削弱士氣既效果<br />\n3. 唔叫都叫咗，而加先改都已經遲<br />\n4. 突然唔叫咪重心虛？<br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n如果真係被spin做港獨又真係會影響民意<br />\n始終香港人都係好避忌呢個話題，中立/淺黃/倒戈的淺藍/被槍嚇醒既深藍，呢d人好容易會被政府帶風向<br />\n我知有d手足已經唔想咁care民意，但如果可以梗係保得就保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我認為可以：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣</span></span></strong><br />\n一向想keep民意最好既方法就係解釋，要向core抗爭者以外既人解釋我地既理念<br />\n做到<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">控制輿論</span>，要快過政府<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">咁重要既口號，上晒外國報紙，有返幾張文宣都好正路，係咪？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁問題來了<br />\n「光復香港 時代革命」呢個口號既具體內容其實係咩呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n抛下磚<br />\n我認為文宣應該將呢個口號link落我地既最終目標<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真正雙普選</span></strong></div><br />\n呢個相信係最多人既共識<br />\n如果做到雙普選，呢個政府一定有機會重新改革，話係「革命」我覺得不為過<br />\n（最敏感應該係「革命」呢粒字，要重點解釋）<br />\n同時，亦都必須link落雙普選既<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>合法性</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係基本法應承我地架</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係中共當年承諾架</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係合法架</span><br />\n<br />\n大家認唔認同呢個方向？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a75052d1a8e6c05f3d7b617fb61458bd03bcee1","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:29:35.000Z","msg":"討論下？"},{"pid":"18843ea0a5edcb1e37462a6842e1d659e649755f","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:30:22.000Z","msg":"777又出招，我地接招化解"},{"pid":"924bf42f524fb8567d471ffc9ffec70b01f52f02","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔好自我審查，但唔好對潛在問題視而不見"},{"pid":"b395c100f1d37a23b71c0d3aef9dc2f29134d46d","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:32:31.000Z","msg":"諗辦法令呢句口號既認受性提升，點都有好處"},{"pid":"8f9353033476240beab19b16e616fd23d622f41e","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee55d32f5e5bc2b256d0186a359c65b2083b4b2","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc7ddcefd3636df40273415a7b570ebbaaf43e09","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:34:21.000Z","msg":"我地自己明既唔代表出面d人都get到"},{"pid":"17b10a740b1155beea78287e55294a19fb9585a0","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:34:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a089d590e3be0732006f47b661121f46b8eeffa","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:35:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ebc755a6639e6e697fc0d386c72128c0c371662","tid":1417377,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"推"},